OL,4,CTech giants targeted over VAT payments
OL,5, The government is to take steps to stop
OL,6, VAT avoidance by multinationals that
OL,7, shelter their income abroad and also by
OL,8, sellers on online websites.
OL,10,FFrom April 2019, companies such as
OL,11,FGoogle, Amazon and Apple will have to
OL,12,Fpay tax on royalties relating to sales
OL,13,Fthey make in the UK.
OL,15,FThe move is expected to bring in B#200m
OL,16,Fa year on average.
OL,18,FHMRC will also be able to hold online
OL,19,Fmarketplaces responsible for any unpaid
OL,20,FVAT for all traders on their platforms.
